      <li><strong>Fire Suppression Systems</strong>: Kitchen, Gas-Based, Water Mist Systems.</li>
      <li><strong>Emergency Lighting & Exit Signs</strong>: LED Exit Signs, Emergency Lights.</li>
      <li><strong>Fire Fighting Equipment</strong>: Fire Hose Reels, Hydrants, Fire Blankets.</li>
      <li><strong>Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)</strong>: Fire Helmets, Gloves, Safety Boots, Fire Suits.</li>
      <li><strong>First Aid and Rescue Tools</strong>: First Aid Kits, Stretchers, Life Jackets.</li>
      <li><strong>Smoke and Gas Detectors</strong>: Carbon Monoxide Detectors, LPG Leak Detectors.</li>
